<h1 id="welcome">Welcome</h1>

<p><a href="https://bws.ninja">Blockchain Web Services</a> is a cloud platform offering a set of products that will help you bring the confidence you need for operations, business processes, and all kinds of interactions requiring a certified trust. We want to build the new <strong>Internet of Trust</strong> by delivering consolidated services enabling you to interact with blockchain smart contracts and ledger databases with a simplified API-oriented approach.</p>
